Detailed Description

This structure is used by the BigWorld client callback system.

It records a single callback request.

Member Function Documentation

bool Script::TimerRecord::operator< ( const TimerRecord &  b  )  const [inline]

This method returns whether or not the input record occurred later than this one.

Returns:
True if input record is earlier (higher priority), false otherwise.
